LARDD 1
TITLE Core Driver Bundle
TEXT Combined RXR bundle for the current in-kernel driver implementations.
SECTION Files
ITEM core-drivers.rxr -> installs drv-rtl8139.drfl, drv-piix3ide.drfl, and driverctl.rxe.
SECTION Install
ITEM rxr verify A:core-drivers.rxr
ITEM rxr install A:core-drivers.rxr
ITEM drivers reload
ITEM drivers show rtl8139
ITEM drivers show ata-pio
ITEM drivers
ITEM sync
END
